steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"16a3f","text":"The following sub-steps are the process for homology-based predictions to identify repetitive elements in the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii genome assembly.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":160},{"style":"italic","offset":110,"length":33}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"72kec","text":"Identify known repetitive elements by aligning the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii  genome sequences against the Repbase-derived RepeatMasker libraries using RepeatMasker (v4.1.0).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":51,"length":33}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"mvps","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"4e5it","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":[]},{"key":"7au6c","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"","data":{"blocks":[{"data":[],"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dl81e","text":"Use the parameters \"-nolow -norna -no is\" when running RepeatMasker.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2f8fg","text":"Identify known repetitive elements by aligning the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii  genome sequences against the transposable element protein database using RepeatProteinMask (an application within the RepeatMasker package)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":51,"length":33}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"c1c2q","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"4d87e","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":[]},{"key":"e1ijg","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"","data":{"blocks":[{"data":[],"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"dvmk1","text":"Use the parameters \"-noLowSimple -pvalue 0.0001 -engine ncbi\" when running RepeatProteinMask.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4jhio","text":"The following sub-steps are the process for de novo predictions to identify repetitive elements in the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii genome assembly.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":153},{"style":"italic","offset":44,"length":7},{"style":"italic","offset":103,"length":33}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"bl2o6","text":"Execute RepeatModeler  (v2.0, RRID:SCR_015027) on the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii assembly to build a de novo  repeat library for this species.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":54,"length":34},{"style":"italic","offset":108,"length":8}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"q4fo","text":"Employ RepeatMasker (v4.1.0) to align the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii genome sequences against the de novo library for repetitive element identification.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"italic","offset":42,"length":34},{"style":"italic","offset":105,"length":8}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"1bkiv","text":"Identify tandem repeats in the Limnodynastes dumerilii dumerilii genome assembly by Tandem Repeats Finder (v4.09).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":114},{"style":"italic","offset":31,"length":34}],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"86nv2","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]},{"key":"3g1uq","text":" ","type":"atomic","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":[]},{"key":"7qvrl","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":[]}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"notes","mutability":"","data":{"blocks":[{"data":[],"depth":0,"entityRanges":[],"inlineStyleRanges":[],"key":"7d06i","text":"Use the parameters \"Match=2 Mismatch=7 Delta=7 PM=80 PI=10 Minscore=50 MaxPeriod=2000\" when running Tandem Repeats Finder.","type":"unstyled"}],"entityMap":{}}}}}
